{"tid":1618091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做奶共藍絲真係好著數","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:14:22.000Z","uid":74237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fddadf3de1e7c98d04b85c2aff30bbca8d065670","tid":1618091,"uid":74237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:05:26.000Z","msg":"個個戴撚住光環屌鳩班後生仔搞亂香港<br />\n你班廢柴就乜撚都唔洗做 假若抗爭成功時 <br />\n你班契弟就坐享義士手足們用血淚換返黎既成果<br />\n<br />\n有個識左十幾年既朋友 個時居然612都唔知發生咩事都可以唔知<br />\n<br />\n本身都知你係藍 但因為要取悅老闆 係社交平台發怖啲藍絲偉論<br />\n<br />\n見到你就覺得嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底藍絲們可以有幾低賤？"},{"pid":"280f70e33839f46cbfbdcc2bda2e6b741f863276","tid":1618091,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"人一藍，腦便殘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adba8549e9ca8c08177053666cba5e2e28da310","tid":1618091,"uid":74237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280f70e33839f46cbfbdcc2bda2e6b741f863276","tid":1618091,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"人一藍，腦便殘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"我已經唔識點面對呢位朋友"},{"pid":"1e1c03767dd772426ded7a21ed5911a4c7580595","tid":1618091,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"唔緊要, 有民主其實對佢地黎講係大懲罰黎<br />\n而家你會見到佢地其實係小數 (一定唔過半)<br />\n有民主之後就係我地既天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔駛怕爭取民主會益左佢地"},{"pid":"a638fd965b761a16a8b96351f38fffc7811617f3","tid":1618091,"uid":74237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"上星期食飯 你仲要吹噓自已入左save hk個谷<br />\n你好自豪咁講你一個藍絲留言有4千幾讚<br />\n作為你朋友 見到你為啲讚而開心 我真係覺得你好仆街"},{"pid":"16c94301417dec111354da8257f3b75497d11b03","tid":1618091,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-